### 1. Register Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Roop Sai",
  "email": "roop@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. Register Manager
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Manager",
  "email": "john@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

### 3. Register Employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jane Employee",
  "email": "jane@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "EMPLOYEE"
}

### 4. Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "roop@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 5. Login with wrong password (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "roop@axiora.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 6. Register duplicate email (409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Roop Sai",
  "email": "roop@axiora.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 7. Register missing fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "",
  "email": "",
  "password": "",
  "role": null
}

### 8. Deactivate user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/deactivate/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}